  (str department) (str `Department of Heavy Industry`)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to provide for the acquisition and transfer of the undertaking of the Richardson and Cruddas Limited, for the reconstruction of the register of its members and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`)
